{"type":"info-page","slug":"mic/content/early/2012/11/16/mic.0.062711-0.abstract","journal":"mic","canonical":"https://www.sgmjournals.org/mic/content/early/2012/11/16/mic.0.062711-0.abstract","title":"Microbiology","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"article abstract-view\">\n\n        <h1 id=\"article-title-1\">DNA unmasked in the red rain cells of Kerala</h1>\n        <div class=\"contributors\">\n          <ol class=\"contributor-list\" id=\"contrib-group-1\">\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-1\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/mic/search?author1=Rajkumar+Gangappa&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">Rajkumar Gangappa</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-1-1\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-1\"></a> and\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"last\" id=\"contrib-2\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/mic/search?author1=Stuart+Hogg&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">Stuart Hogg</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-1-2\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-1\"></a><a id=\"xref-corresp-1-1\" class=\"xref-fn\" href=\"#corresp-1\">1</a>\n            </li>\n          </ol>\n          <ol class=\"affiliation-list\">\n            <li class=\"aff\">\n              <a id=\"aff-1\" name=\"aff-1\"></a>\n              <address>\n                <sup></sup> University of Glamorgan\n              </address>\n            </li>\n          </ol>\n          <ol class=\"corresp-list\">\n            <li class=\"corresp\" id=\"corresp-1\">\n              <a class=\"rev-xref\" href=\"#xref-corresp-1-1\">↵</a><sup>1</sup> E-mail: <span class=\"em-link\"><span class=\"em-addr\">sihogg{at}glam.ac.uk</span></span>\n            </li>\n          </ol>\n\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"section abstract\" id=\"abstract-1\">\n          <h2>Abstract</h2>\n          <p id=\"p-1\">Extraordinary claims have been made for the biological properties of the red rain cells of Kerala, including a suggestion that they lack DNA. We have investigated the fluorescence properties of red rain cells, and the solubility of the red pigment in a variety of solvents. Extraction of the pigment with DMSO allowed successful staining of DNA using DAPI. Cellular impermeability to staining reagents due to the red pigment is the likely explanation for the failure of previous efforts to demonstrate DNA in red rain cells.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"social-bookmarking\">\n        <ul class=\"social-bookmark-links\">\n          <li class=\"social-bookmarking-item social-bookmarking-item-citeulike\">\n            <a href=\"/mic/external-ref?tag_url=http://mic.sgmjournals.org/cgi/content/long/mic.0.062711-0v1&amp;title=DNA%20unmasked%20in%20the%20red%20rain%20cells%20of%20Kerala+--+Gangappa%20and%20Hogg+--+MIC&amp;doi=10.1099/mic.0.062711-0&amp;link_type=CITEULIKE\"><img src=\"/shared/img/common/social-bookmarking/citeulike.gif\" alt=\"Add to CiteULike\" title=\"CiteULike\"></a><span class=\"soc-bm-link-text\">CiteULike</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"social-bookmarking-item social-bookmarking-item-connotea\">\n            <a href=\"/mic/external-ref?tag_url=http://mic.sgmjournals.org/cgi/content/long/mic.0.062711-0v1&amp;title=DNA%20unmasked%20in%20the%20red%20rain%20cells%20of%20Kerala+--+Gangappa%20and%20Hogg+--+MIC&amp;doi=10.1099/mic.0.062711-0&amp;link_type=CONNOTEA\"><img src=\"/shared/img/common/social-bookmarking/connotea.gif\" alt=\"Add to Connotea\" title=\"Connotea\"></a><span class=\"soc-bm-link-text\">Connotea</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"social-bookmarking-item social-bookmarking-item-delicious\">\n            <a href=\"/mic/external-ref?tag_url=http://mic.sgmjournals.org/cgi/content/long/mic.0.062711-0v1&amp;title=DNA%20unmasked%20in%20the%20red%20rain%20cells%20of%20Kerala+--+Gangappa%20and%20Hogg+--+MIC&amp;doi=10.1099/mic.0.062711-0&amp;link_type=DEL_ICIO_US\"><img src=\"/shared/img/common/social-bookmarking/delicious.gif\" alt=\"Add to Deli